<p>[Page 16]</p>
<p>Wednesday 3/4/18&nbsp; Moved by circuitous route to Meteren by Bus- billeted</p>
<p>Thursday 4/4/18&nbsp; Heavy day entraining early in morning&nbsp; bought some lace for Doff</p>
<p>Friday 5/4/18&nbsp; Left Meteren at 3 am entrained at Caistre 6 am arrived Amiens 9 p.m. marched to Allonville</p>
<p>Saturday 6/4/18 marched to La Neuvelle &amp; billeted for night.</p>
<p>Sunday 7/4/18 Marched to [Bazieux?] [Baisieux] &amp; relieved Imlay&#39;s lot, moved forward to Support at night relieving Christie.</p>
<p>Monday 8/4/18&nbsp; Raining heavily all night&nbsp; Hun shelling all day&nbsp; about 10 casualties</p>
